OL,3,CMan found with cocaine and heroin on
OL,4,CM6 jailed
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 44 months in prison for possession
OL,8,Fwith intent to supply Class A drugs.
OL,10,FMark McAvoy from Paisley was stopped
OL,11,Fby police as he was driving between
OL,12,Fjunctions 39 and 40 on the M6 near
OL,13,FCarlisle, on December 31 2025.
OL,15,FAn officer searched McAvoy's Vauxhall
OL,16,FInsignia and found a cardboard box in
OL,17,Fthe boot, in which he discovered ten
OL,18,Fwrapped bricks of cocaine.
