OL,6,FTwo further bags of cocaine were then
OL,7,Ffound, adding up to a total of 11.5
OL,8,Fkilograms of cocaine in the vehicle.
OL,10,FPolice also discovered 37 grams of a
OL,11,Fbrown powder, which tests later
OL,12,Frevealed to be heroin.
OL,14,FMcAvoy was arrested and charged with
OL,15,Ftwo counts of possession of Class A
OL,16,Fdrugs, offences which he later
OL,17,Fadmitted at court.
OL,19,FMcAvoy was sentenced to 44 months'
OL,20,Fimprisonment at Carlisle Crown Court
OL,21,Fon February 19, 2026.
