OL,6,FDetective Constable Hugh Poward of
OL,7,FCumbria Police said: "This is the
OL,8,Flatest example of our officers
OL,9,Fstopping a vehicle travelling through
OL,10,Fthe county and uncovering evidence of
OL,11,Fpossession with intent to supply Class
OL,12,FA drugs offences.
OL,14,F"This stop resulted in a significant
OL,15,Famount of drugs being recovered and a
OL,16,Fprison sentence being handed down by
OL,17,Fthe courts.
